reviewText: Very quaint.  Does not live up to its title of American Nudes.  But then it is from the 1950's so typical.

Everyone would be pleasantly surprised by the explicit nudity of the spots in question which is not commensurate with the standards of that era ( we are talking about the '40 's! ). As far as I am concered, I expected to find more laces, underware, peticoats, stockings, garters and suspender belts. Something like burlesque that is. Nontheless I fully recommend the product to the customers of your site.
